Version 1.0 BETA 3: December 9, 2011 - Fixed issue 6

Version 1.0 BETA 2: October 3, 2011 - Fixed issues 4 and 5
	NOTE: Issue 5 dealt with significant refactoring of the code.  There is no direct upgrade path
	available between BETA 1 and BETA 2 because of the changes in services and database schemas.
	You will need to manually remove all MC_* tables from the database prior to deploying this updated 
	portlet. 

